  ;; ============================================================
  ;; BLOCK 4 — INA219 CURRENT MONITOR  (origin ~152, 115)
  ;; U3: INA219xIDCNT  (I2C current/power monitor, SOT-23-8)
  ;;   Monitors the 1.2V core rail current via R7 shunt
  ;; R7: 100mΩ shunt resistor (2512, 1% 1W)
  ;;   Full-scale 3.2A → Vshunt = 320mV (INA219 max ±320mV or ±40mV range)
  ;; R8, R9: I2C address pull-downs (A0=GND, A1=GND → addr 0x40)
  ;; C11, C12: bypass caps
